ICRefreshInventoryCubes_ST is a SecurityClass
	description is "Refresh Inventory Cubes"
	Access Rights
		
		InventoryTransactionLine BusinessClass
			is accessible
				for UpdateInventoryCubes
				when (Company.SecurityGroupAllowsAccess)

		RefreshInventoryCubes MenuItem for InventoryManagerMenu Menu
			is accessible 
				for all actions
				unconditionally
		
				